package uz.mymax.savvyenglish.utils

var text = "<p>\uD83D\uDCA1Collocations of the day \uD83D\uDC4C</p>\n" +
        "<p>✳️ Today in this post we are going to learn the collocations with the word 'custom' (odat, an'ana).</p>\n" +
        "<p>✅ accepted/age-old/ancient/established/traditional/local custom - qabul qilingan/eski/qadimiy/o'rnatilgan/an'anaviy/mahalliy odat<br />\uD83D\uDD38It's an ancient custom which is beginning to die out. (Bu yo'qolib borayotgan qadimiy odatdir)<br />✅ to follow/observe/respect a custom - odatga amal qilmoq/odatni hurmat qilmoq <br />\uD83D\uDD38They still follow the custom of pinning money to the bride's dress. (Ular haligacha kelinning ko'ylagiga pul taqish odatiga amal qilishadi)<br />✅ to maintain/preserve/revive a custom - odatni saqlab qolmoq/qayta tiklamoq<br />\uD83D\uDD38 Traditional customs are being revived. (An'anaviy odatlar qayta tiklanmoqda)<br />✅ according to a custom/in accordance with a custom - odatga muvofiq<br />\uD83D\uDD38They poured wine round the trees in accordance with local custom. (Ular mahalliy odatga muvofiq daraxtning atrofiga musallas to'kishdi)<br />✅ as is/was the custom - odat bo'lgani uchun<br />\uD83D\uDD38People throw coins onto the stage, as was the custom. (Odamlar odat bo'lgani uchun sahnaga tanga uloqtirishadi)</p>"

